						<div class="postbody">ChangeLog:
<br />NESICIDE &amp; standalone emulator V1.001
<br />Fixed problem where non-ASCII keys used for controller configuration were not being mapped correctly.
<br />
<br />(Thanks, dwedit!)
<br />
<br />EDIT: Doh, I just re-read and forgot to try SHIFT.  Unfortunately those come across as modifiers not keystrokes so it looks like I've still got a bit of work to do to support CTRL, SHIFT, and ALT being used as emulator keys.</div>

