						<div class="postbody">The best way to map keys is...
<br />
<br />W-Up
<br />S-Down
<br />A-Left
<br />D-Right
<br />L-A
<br />K-B
<br />G-Start
<br />F-Select
<br />
<br />so you don't lose feeling. But that's just IMO. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /> Besides being a bare-bones emulator and not supporting the stuff I need [Vaus emulation] I can't use it, but it seems nice. How accurate is it?</div>

